sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as API Client
    participant Server as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Auth as AuthN Middleware<br/>(OAuth2 JWT / Custom)
    participant OIDC as OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Quota as Quota Middleware
    participant ABAC as Access Control<br/>(Cedar ABAC)
    participant Inference as Inference Router
    participant Agent as Agent Provider
    participant Safety as Safety Router
    participant RAG as RAG Tool Runtime
    participant vLLM as vLLM Provider<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant VectorDB as pgvector<br/>5432/TCP PostgreSQL
    participant SQLite as SQLite<br/>(Persistence)

    Note over Client,SQLite: Flow 1: Chat Completion Request

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/inference/chat-completion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (JWT)
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth->>OIDC: Fetch JWKS / Introspect token<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+
    OIDC-->>Auth: Token claims (sub, groups, roles)
    Auth->>Quota: Check rate limit
    Quota->>ABAC: Evaluate access policy
    ABAC->>Inference: Route to provider
    Inference->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer Token, Configurable TLS
    vLLM-->>Inference: Completion response (SSE stream)
    Inference-->>Server: Stream tokens
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response<br/>HTTP/HTTPS

    Note over Client,SQLite: Flow 2: Agent Turn with Tool Use (RAG)

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/agents/{id}/turn<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>Agent: Create agent turn
    Agent->>Inference: Initial chat-completion (in-process)
    Inference->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>Inference: Response with tool_call(rag_query)
    Inference-->>Agent: Tool call detected

    Agent->>RAG: Execute RAG query (in-process)
    RAG->>VectorDB: SELECT with vector similarity<br/>5432/TCP, Configurable TLS, User/Pass
    VectorDB-->>RAG: Relevant document chunks
    RAG-->>Agent: RAG context

    Agent->>Inference: Chat-completion with RAG context (in-process)
    Inference->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>+ retrieved context
    vLLM-->>Inference: Final response
    Inference-->>Agent: Completion
    Agent->>SQLite: Persist session/turn
    Agent-->>Server: Agent turn result
    Server-->>Client: SSE stream response

    Note over Client,SQLite: Flow 3: Safety Shield Execution

    Client->>Server: POST /v1/safety/run-shield<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Server->>Auth: Validate token
    Auth-->>Server: Authenticated
    Server->>Safety: Route to safety provider
    Safety->>vLLM: Inference with Llama Guard model<br/>Bearer Token
    vLLM-->>Safety: Safety classification
    Safety-->>Server: Shield result (safe/unsafe + violation)
    Server-->>Client: Shield response
